This repository contains various small scripts that I have written to automate my day-to-day activities.
Each script is maintained in its own branch for ease of maintenance.

These scripts are free for personal use. You may modify them as you want as long as the modification is valid under the GPL.

For any changes, please fork the repository and send a pull request.
For anything else, please contact me on my mail id: Darshit Shah <darnir@gmail.com>
